            </div>
              <div class="tab-pane" id="quang-dang" role="tabpanel">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-lg-8 details order-2 order-lg-1">
                    <h3>URGENT TRANSITION: ACCELERATING EMISSION CUTS FOR A RENEWABLE FUTURE</h3>
                    <p class="fst-italic"> 
                     <span> Switching energy systems from fossil fuels to renewables like solar or wind will reduce the emissions driving climate change. But we have to start right now. While a growing coalition of countries is committing to net zero emissions by 2050, about half of emissions cuts must be in place by 2030 to keep warming below 1.5°C. Fossil fuel production must decline by roughly 6 percent per year between 2020 and 2030
                     </span>
                      </p>
                      <p style="text-align:right;">- Vu Quang Dang _Sandbox JTC -</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
